review_data: Reviewed in the United States on September 4, 2018

title: Great firm, plain Greek yoghurt, excellent as a sour cream substitute!
review: I always have some of this going for desserts, smoothies and for going with savory snacks like nachos and baked potatoes.It's a super creamy consistency with a nice level of tartness.It has a nice firmness to it.Delivery was well packed and came prompt from the UK to the US.
